        Welcome!
        This tutorial will walk you through the basics of the Dive platform, and show you everything you need to know
        But first, we would like to tell you how our platform was designed to help you learn.
        At Dive, it doesn't matter where you start, or how quickly you learn the materials. All that matters is that everyday you learn and discover a little more than the day before!
        It is important to realize that making mistakes is apart of any learning process. At Dive you will not be punished for mistakes. //fix this
