        This is the home menu for Dive. From here you will be able to visit and do a variety of things, let's go throught them!
        To continue, simply click the blue box


        Your Character
        This is your customizable Dive character. You can change him/her however you like! If you wan to add a little extra you can buy him gear from the Dive shop!


        Dive Level
        As you begin to earn more Dive points from learning and exploring, you will begin to level up!
        As you level up, you will have access to better prizes, and earn more Dive points!


        Dive Points
        As you learn and discover more, you will be rewarded with Dive points. You can use Dive points to purchase things from the shop!


